Hi All! I have a webview in my application that Im loading with 
```
loadDataWithBaseURL(mBasePath, mContent, "text/html", "utf-8", null);
```
where mBasePath is the root folder saved on the device which contains two files, “Default.htm” and “animated.gif”. 

mContent is a string representation of the contents of “Default.htm”. I’ve attached the chrome webview debugger to my app and when I inspect the webview, I can see the contents of the webview look like this: 

```
